Package: guppyR
Title: A Shiny input using the Guppy mathematics widget.
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Gregg", "Whitworth", email = "whitworthg@wlu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: HTMLWidgets wrapper adapting the Guppy equation editor for use as an input in Shiny apps. Provides facilities for feedback on equation correctness on the client and sanitized server-side function evaluation.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.3)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
